title.narrative: OUTPUT 1.1.21 ENABLING Early Child Development (ECD) ENVIRONMENT

description.narrative: 1.1.21 MOES ensures increased equity in access to pre-school education, a better quality teaching and learning environment in basic education, and effective responses to the needs of out-of-school children (RKLA 3), which contributes to Early Learning, Equitable Access To Quality Education, Learning Outcomes. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Outcome 1.1 Equitable and Responsive Systems children and women have increased access to quality and responsive services, including social benefits
